description.en-us: Star Wars Starships Select is a line of 1:50 scale replicas of starships from the Star Wars media franchise, acting as a sort of Premium version to the standard Starships line. These versions feature various moving features and are of a larger scale compared to regular Hot Wheels Starships and features an "upgraded" display stand specific to each ship, featuring an etching of the ship's name as well as the logo of its galactic affiliation.
